snippet.title: Tiny Dreams and Ghostly Tunes üéÉ Classical Music for a Cozy Halloween üéÉ Cello and Piano lullabies
snippet.description:
Tonight, the cello will whisper stories of autumn and the full moon, while the piano will embrace each note with gentle warmth.

The melodies are sad, yes, but also filled with calm and hope.

Music to dream to, to drift away, to help the little ones fall asleep wrapped in the magic of Halloween.

May each note bring you a little closer to peace and light and as always, thank you for being here and for all your supportüå±üåü
